OL,3,CMan dies after fire in garden in
OL,4,CCoventry
OL,6,FA man in his 50s has died after a fire
OL,7,Fin a garden in Coventry.
OL,9,FEmergency services were called to
OL,10,FAnglian Way just before 11am on
OL,11,FThursday morning (16 April).
OL,13,FHe was treated for his injuries then
OL,14,Fairlifted to Queen Elizabeth Hospital
OL,15,Fin Birmingham by an air ambulance.
OL,17,FWest Midlands Ambulance said: "We were
OL,18,Fcalled to an incident at a private
OL,19,Faddress on Anglian Way at 10.47am
OL,20,Fyesterday.
