OL,3,CMan dies after fire in garden in
OL,4,CCoventry
OL,6,F"Two ambulances and a helicopter from
OL,7,Fthe Midlands Air Ambulance Charity
OL,8,Fattended the scene.
OL,10,F"On arrival, we discovered one
OL,11,Fpatient, a man. He was treated for
OL,12,Fserious injuries before being
OL,13,Fairlifted to Queen Elizabeth Hospital,
OL,14,FBirmingham."
OL,16,FWest Midlands Police said the man, who
OL,17,Fhas not been identified, is believed
OL,18,Fto be in his 50s.
