OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776463868
OL,3,CMan dies after fire in garden in
OL,4,CCoventry
OL,6,FIn a statement, the force said: "Our
OL,7,Fthoughts are with his family at this
OL,8,Fsad time.
OL,10,F"Following enquiries, the man's death
OL,11,Fis not being treated as suspicious,
OL,12,Fand a report will be prepared for the
OL,13,Fcoroner in due course."
